      <label class="med-gray h5 mb2 block">Instructor</label>
      <div class="flex underline-link mb3">
        <div class="flex-none mr3">
            <img width="80" src="https://hackdesign.imgix.net/curators/moizsyed@2x.jpg?ixlib=rails-2.1.4&dpr=2&w=80&h=80&fit=crop&fm=jpeg&auto=format&mask=ellipse&s=d598173cd1ed3d6f4599b6e9eaaee9c0" alt="Moizsyed@2x.jpg?ixlib=rails 2.1" />
        </div>
        <div class="flex-auto">
          <h5 class="h3 mt0 mb1 regular dark-blue">Moiz Syed</h5>
          <h5 class="h4 mt0 mb1 med-gray regular">
              Designer, 
              <a target="_blank" href="http://hipmunk.com">Hipmunk</a>
          </h5>
          <p class="med-gray">I'm a designer at <a href="http://www.hipmunk.com" target="_blank">Hipmunk</a>. Previously, I was pushing pixels and disturbing the peace at <a href="http://www.drawbrid.ge" target="_blank">Drawbridge</a>, <a href="http://www.citrix.com" target="_blank">Citrix Systems</a> and <a href="http://www.ibminteractive.com" target="_blank">IBM Interactive</a>. On my weekends, I try to write code to justify the three semesters of computer science I once did. I grew up in Toronto where I went to design school at <a href="http://design.yorku.ca" target="_blank">York University</a>. You can see some of my really old work <a href="http://www.moiz.ca" target="_blank">here</a> or <a href="http://www.twitter.com/moizsyed" target="_blank">find me on twitter</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>


